text.head:
Order
12/05/2021
text.p:
Learned counsel for the applicant submits that the office has
wrongly registered the bail application all over again after
registering the same as S.B. Criminal Miscellaneous Bail
Application No. 6097/2021 and, therefore, the same may be
permitted to be withdrawn with liberty to pursue S.B. Criminal
Miscellaneous Bail Application No. 6097/2021.
In view of the submissions made, the present bail application
is dismissed as withdrawn with liberty as aforesaid.
